OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777395954
OL,3,CNew IRA claims responsibility for
OL,4,CDunmurry car bomb attack
OL,6,FThe New IRA has claimed responsibility
OL,7,Ffor the car bomb attack on Dunmurry
OL,8,Fpolice station on Saturday.
OL,10,FThe dissident republican group made
OL,11,Fthe claim through a statement to the
OL,12,FIrish News.
OL,14,FThe newspaper reported the dissident
OL,15,Frepublican group claim that the attack
OL,16,Fhad been an attempt to kill police
OL,17,Fofficers as they tried to leave the
OL,18,Fstation.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
