FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777395954
OL,3,CNew IRA claims responsibility for
OL,4,CDunmurry car bomb attack
OL,6,FA PSNI spokesperson said: "We are
OL,7,Faware of the claim and the
OL,8,Finvestigation remains ongoing."
OL,10,FMeanwhile, high visibility policing
OL,11,Foperation is to be launched across
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland to counter the
OL,13,Fdissident republican threat, a senior
OL,14,Fofficer has said.
OL,16,FPSNI Assistant Chief Constable Davy
OL,17,FBeck said the policing operation would
OL,18,Finvolve more vehicle checkpoints and
OL,19,Fofficers on patrol which "may cause
OL,20,Fsome inconvenience to the general
OL,21,Fpublic".
OL,26,@nD@[OUpD@_O]{D@ZOU}D@GO]
