PN,44303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777395954
OL,3,CNew IRA claims responsibility for
OL,4,CDunmurry car bomb attack
OL,6,FThere has been widespread political
OL,7,Fcondemnation of the incident in which
OL,8,Fa male delivery driver was hijacked in
OL,9,Fthe Twinbrook area of west Belfast.
OL,11,FA device was placed inside the vehicle
OL,12,Fand he was ordered to drive to
OL,13,FDunmurry police station.
OL,15,FThe car exploded outside the station
OL,16,Fas people were being evacuated. Nobody
OL,17,Fwas injured.
OL,19,FPolice are treating the incident as
OL,20,Fattempted murder.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
