FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777395954
OL,3,CNew IRA claims responsibility for
OL,4,CDunmurry car bomb attack
OL,6,FIt happened just weeks after an
OL,7,Fattempted car bomb attack on Lurgan
OL,8,Fpolice station.
OL,10,FOn Tuesday Mr Beck said: "Communities
OL,11,Facross Northern Ireland will see an
OL,12,Fincrease in policing activity as a
OL,13,Fhigh visibility policing operation
OL,14,Fgets under way to counter the ongoing
OL,15,Fdissident threat.
OL,26,@rD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777395954
OL,3,CNew IRA claims responsibility for
OL,4,CDunmurry car bomb attack
OL,6,F"We have concerns about threats across
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland from dissident
OL,8,Fgroups, particularly in the wake of
OL,9,Fthe recent attack on Dunmurry police
OL,10,Fstation, which demonstrated a clear
OL,11,Fintent to damage and disrupt
OL,12,Fcommunities and potentially injure and
OL,13,Fkill police officers and staff.
OL,15,F"Our job is to keep communities safe
OL,16,Fand also our officers who bravely
OL,17,Fserve to protect these communities.
OL,19,F"We are taking every reasonable step
OL,20,Fto do so. However, we need the active
OL,21,Fsupport of our communities to do this."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU{D@AOU}D@gO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777395954
OL,3,CNew IRA claims responsibility for
OL,4,CDunmurry car bomb attack
OL,6,FHe added: "This operation will involve
OL,7,Fmore vehicle checkpoints and
OL,8,Fpatrolling officers.
OL,10,F"This may cause some inconvenience to
OL,11,Fthe general public, however, we are
OL,12,Fasking for patience and the support of
OL,13,Fcommunities as we work hard to keep us
OL,14,Fall safe."
OL,16,FOn Monday, the PSNI released footage
OL,17,Fof the moment the car bomb exploded.
OL,19,FThe footage shows a person walking
OL,20,Falong a path before a large flash of
OL,21,Flight erupts ahead.
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@AOUvD@JO]
