OL,3,CNew IRA claims responsibility for
OL,4,CDunmurry car bomb attack
OL,6,FThe dissident republican attack has
OL,7,Fbeen condemned by Northern Ireland's
OL,8,Fpolitical leaders and chief constable,
OL,9,Fwho voiced their condemnation at a
OL,10,Fjoint press conference on Monday.
